        On Question, Whether Clause 9 shall stand part of the Bill?
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0629P0-04275'>
        <a name='S5LV0629P0_20011210_GCR_80'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-joan-hanham' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
