        [<span class="italic">Amendment No. 40 not moved.</span>]
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0629P0-04370'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0629P0_20011210_GCR_175' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Schedule 2 agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0629P0-04371'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0629P0_20011210_GCR_176' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
